schools.name: Manhattan Middle School Of The Arts And Academics

data.description: With Stunning Views of the Flatirons, this charming ranch style home with oversized 2-car garage has endless opportunities.  Sitting on a large corner lot, this property offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, large living room with brick fireplace, dining room and eat-in-kitchen.  Remodel the inside or put on an addition.  This prime location is only minutes from CU Boulder Campus, the flatirons, shopping and great dining.You don't want to miss it!
